quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  3,101,"E ko honno yeddirton Alla …ďaawo nde gom…óin…óon Mo, nde tawnoo hi…óon jogitii sabu …ďur…óo mawnude e ko tabitton ka gom…óinal?! Hi…óon jannganeede Aayeeje Alla …óen, Nulaa…óo Makko on Muhammadu on mo jam e kisiyee woni e mun on no …ďannginana on …óe, kala on jogitor…óo Deftere Alla nden e sunna Nulaa…óo Makko on; gom…óii Alla Fewnirii Mo faade e laawol foccii ngol, ngol oonyaaki."
  3,102,"Ko onon yogom…óim…ďe Alla e Nulaa…óo Makko on, huliree Alla no O Haaniri non hulireede; ko …óum woni …óoftagol Yamirooje Makko …óen wo…ó…óitoon ha…óaa…ói Makko …óin, jaarna Mo e Neemaaji Makko …óin, jogito…óon Diina Makko kan haa maayde nden ara on e hoore …óum."
  3,103,"Jogitee onon Muumini en, Deftere nden e sunna on, wata on faggito ko senndata on. Annditee Neema Alla on e dow moo…óon tuma laatino…óon anyandiru…ďe ado lislaamu on, hara o warindira e famdude e sababuuji , O renndini …ďer…óe mon …óen e lislaamu on, wontir…óon ∆Āural Makko ngal si…ó…óu…ďe ka diina, yurmondir…ďe wallindiroo…ďe. On laatinoke ko adii …óum, …ďa…ótornoo…ďe naatugol yiite ngen fii keeferaaku mo'on; Alla Da…óndiri mon-nge sabu lislaamu on, O Fewniri on liimaanu. Ko wano Alla ∆Āannginirani on nii …óum …óoo, O ∆ĀannginiraŇčta on kon ko mo∆ī∆īinanta- on fiyakuuji mo'on aduna e laakara; fii yo on feewir e laawol peewal ngol, jokkon laawol foccii ngol ngol."
  3,104,"Yo laato e mo'on onon Muumini en, jamaa nodday…óo e kala mo∆ī∆īere nden Alla Yi…ói, …ďe yamira mo∆ī∆īere nde sari'a on tinndi e mu'un haqqille …óen ja…ďi, …ďe ha…óa kadi ko a√Īinii kon ko sari'a on ha…ói haqqille …óen √Īiddini fii mun. ∆Āen siforii…ďe …óin sifaaji, ko …ďen woni yim…ďe malaa…ďe …ďen aduna e laakara."
  3,105,"Onon Muumini en, wata on laato wa yim…ďe Defte …ďen sertu…ďe …ďe wonti pelle e dente, …ďe luutondiri e diina ma…ď…ďe kan …ďaawo nde Aayeeje …ďanngu…óe …óen ari e ma…ď…ďe immorde ka Alla Toowu…óo On. ∆Āen jaŇčtaa…ďe …óon, no woodani …ďe lepte sa…ótu…óe immorde ka Alla."
  3,106,"∆äee lepte sa…ótu…óe …óoo he…ďay…ďe √Īalnde darngal tuma geece yim…ďe gom…óinal …ďen ranwoyta welo-welo e maloore, geece heefer…ďe …ďen …ďawlira suno e aannde. Si ko …ďen …ďe geece mu'un …ďawli nden √Īalnde mawnde, …ďe feliroyte wi'eede: "E on yeddu bajjin…óingol Alla ngol e Ahadi Makko ndin, ndi O Ahodi e mo'on wonnde on kafidataa Mo hay e huunde, ja…ďu…óon …óum qirriti…óon?! Awa mee…óee lepte Alla …óen …óe O Hebilani on sabu keeferaaku mo'on."
  3,107,"Si tawii ko …ďen …ďe geece mu'un rawni, werde ma…ď…ďe nden ko neemaaji Aljanna, duumotoo…ďe ton poomaa; e neemaaji …ói lannataa."
  3,108,"∆äee …óoo Aayeeje yowitii…óe e Fodoore Alla e Kammbol Makko; Me…óen Janngirane …óe an Annabiijo, e hoore goonga ka humpitugol, e ka nun…óugol ka √Īaawooje. Alla wonaali Faandanii…óo hay gooto e winndere nden too√Īe, si ko woni, O Leptirtaa go…ó…óo si wanaa ko o faggitii kon."